Dialogs.Dialog: Rinko
Hey, why are you dating Rinko？
Why do you ask？
It was suddenly on my mind. Like, what part of me do you admire...？
Well... You're mean. You aren't honest to your feelings. You're really obstinate...
...Hey, I was asking about the good things you like about me.
Don't be silly. All I said were cute things. You're just so innocent, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hmm... You have such weird taste！
That's cruel. My girlfriend likes to say things that hurt my feelings.
What's that？ Are you an idiot！？
Rinko
I've asked you before, but...
Hmm？ What is it？
About the reason you're dating Rinko...
...Yeah.
Don't you have any reason that's easy to understand？ Come on！ Like, because Rinko is so cute~ Or because Rinko is pretty~
Ah！ Your eyes are cute.
My eyes...？
Yes. You have really long eyelashes that naturally curl up.
Hmm？ Since when did you pay that much attention to my face？
Um, well... When we kissed.
Idiot！ You should've closed your eyes at that time！
Sorry...
Rinko
How do you define "love"？
Why do you ask all of a sudden？
Well... I think this is difficult.
Hmm... It's when someone wants to treasure another person, maybe？
What Rinko wanted to ask is not just that... It's something more...
Hmm？
Why does it have to be this one specific person？
About that...
It has to be that one, not the others, right？ This must have something to do with our mental structure.
(You think about something so difficult.)
Rinko
Hey, perhaps, people fall in love because it's human instinct.
Are you talking about what we discussed before？ Why do you say that？
It's the instinct to preserve the human species. It's in our DNA.
That is a fact, but in this case it's, you know ▲小早川＊▲...
A coincidence？
I'd say that it's fate...
What？ Do you mean it was already decided from the beginning？ No, that can't be true. It's Rinko who intentionally chose you.
...Anyway, let's get back to the topic.
Now that I know what you think, I'm satisfied. I don't care about these complicated things, ▲小早川＊▲.
...I think it's okay like this... But love is still something I don't understand...
Rinko
Speaking of which, it's coming up, huh？
What's coming up？
No, never mind.
Well, if you don't know... then that's better for me.
What is it？ Now you're making me curious...
It'd be nice to have a surprise, right？
If it's something good, I'll be happy.
It's something good, I guess.
What is it？ I'm curious...
Now, now. You'll know when it's time！
Rinko
Is there anything you want？
Hmm, I'd wish for better intelligence, fitness, sense, and charm.
What are those...？
...Never mind.
I didn't mean something like that... How about a CD or a book？ Something tangible.
Hmm... What would it be？ I can't think of anything right now...
That troubles me. You have to think about it, okay？
Then I think I want your kiss. How's that, ▲小早川＊▲？
...Pervert.
I'll ask you again. Until then, think about it very carefully.
Rinko
Hey, have you thought about what you want？
Ah, I totally forgot！
Geez, what is this！？ There has to be something you wish for...
But I already have you as my girlfriend now, ▲小早川＊▲.
That's all I've ever wished for...
Hehe... Okay. But I think you still don't get what I mean.
Well, can your girlfriend give you something that would make you happy？
If it's something from my girlfriend, wouldn't I be happy with anything she gives me？
Hmm... Just don't complain about this later then.
Huh？
Rinko
Hey, I think I should ask you...
About...？
Your birthday is coming up, right？
Ah... That's right！ I totally forgot...
At least try to remember your own birthday！
Do you have any plans for your birthday？ Are you gonna eat cake and celebrate it with your family？
Nah. I'm too old to have a birthday party.
I see. But don't you want people to celebrate your birthday？
It'd be nice if my girlfriend would celebrate my birthday with me.
Hmm... I'll think about it then. Hehe.
Okay！
Rinko
It's getting hot lately.
This is what summer is all about！
Well... It's almost August. This is really bad.
Are you sensitive to heat？
Well... Yeah, a little bit, but...
Hmm...？
Hah... It's coming soon. August is coming soon...
Speaking of August, your birthday is coming, right, ▲小早川＊▲？
Eh？ Is that so？ I don't really care about it, so I totally forgot. I see, I see~
(It's your birthday, huh？ What should I do, ▲小早川＊▲？)
Rinko
Rinko is about to be another year older.
Yeah.
I'll be a step closer to becoming an adult.
But don't you feel sad to grow older？
No, not at all.
Ah, I see... I forgot you are a lolicon.
I'm not！
Hmm... Well, just take it as a joke then.
But you want Rinko to become a beautiful woman, right？
For me, the current you is the best, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hmm... Okay...
Rinko
It's coming up... Hehe.
Your birthday, right？
Yeah！
A birthday is such a very important occasion for girls, huh？
For me, it has always been like an "Oh yeah" feeling when my family celebrated it with me.
But this year is gonna be a special birthday！ It's the "Hooray" feeling.
I'm gonna spend my birthday with my boyfriend.
If you're looking forward to it like that, I feel a little pressured...
Yeah？ I'm also anxious that you might not celebrate it with me.
Don't worry about that！
Rinko
Hey... This might be the first time that I'm looking forward to my birthday.
Then I'll try my best to make you happy, ▲小早川＊▲.
Thanks.
So, you have any request？ Is there anything you want？
For my present...？
Just having the one I love say "Happy birthday" to me is more than enough.
Really？ It feels good to look forward to a present from the one you love, right？
Well, not really...
For me, the best present is that I don't have to celebrate my birthday alone.
I see...
Rinko
Do you know what's coming up？
What is it？
Could it be that you really forgot it？
No... Well... What's coming up then？
Hah... This is it...
Are you mad at me？
I'm not mad.
I'm just shocked that you forgot our memorable day.
Too slow！
(It's been a year already...)
Rinko
A lot of things happened during this one year.
Yeah... I wonder how many times you kicked me ▲小早川＊▲...
Hiya！！
Ouch！！
This is the commemorative 100th kick. Congratulations！
...Let's stop the joke. You've always been with me and I feel like I'm so used to having you by my side, ▲小早川＊▲,.
I know that. And for me, my heart still beats fast when I'm with you.
Actually, me too. I still get nervous whenever we kiss...
...Yeah.
Do you want your heart to beat faster now？ How about we kiss here？
Don't get so ahead of yourself！ Do you want to take the 101st kick？
I'm sorry...
Rinko
Our anniversary is coming up.
A year has gone by so fast...
What do you think about me now？ Have your feelings changed？ Do you feel that I'm a bit cooler now？
Nothing has changed at all. I still love you the same way I used to, ▲小早川＊▲.
Really！？ Hehe...
And you？ Have your feelings changed ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko's feelings have changed.
Eh...？ No way.
Compared to the time we started dating, Rinko loves you a lot more, now. So, victory belongs to Rinko.
...Can't it be a draw？
No！
(So, she really loves me...)
Rinko
Hey, thanks for being with Rinko for this whole year.
Why do you say that all of a sudden？
I think you might've had to bear with a lot of things to be with me for a whole year.
I didn't bear with anything.
But Rinko is such a selfish and hot-tempered girl...
Well, you are like that, but I've never felt bad about you at all.
Thanks. Hehe.
Next year, when another year has passed, will we be talking like this...？
Not just next year. The year after that, too...
Yeah. And years after that, forever... okay？
Rinko
Why are you dating Rinko？
Why do you ask all of a sudden？
Because Rinko doesn't act like a girl at all.
Were you forced to say "Okay" when I confessed to you...？
No way.
Really？
Of course. I said "Okay" because I love you ▲小早川＊▲.
Me, too. So, you'd better remember that I'm happy to have you as my boyfriend.
Rinko
Tell me honestly, what part of me do you like？
What is this, all of a sudden？
Because I think you would prefer someone more mature. Rinko is always childish, right？
That's not true.
Or could it be that... you are a lolicon？
No, I'm not！
Then what part of me do you like？
You're not honest with feelings. You're childish. You're selfish...
What is that？ From what you just said, Rinko is such a bad girl, huh？！？
No, those are what I love in my girlfriend.
Why are you saying things like that all of a sudden？
Yeah, yeah. That part of you is also very cute. Did you know that？
You idiot...
Rinko
Love...
Love... When did it start？
Well... I've never thought about it.
At first, we were just strangers.
Yeah...
Before we realized it, we couldn't live without each other...
Yeah...
It's mysterious, isn't it？
You're right... But, we really are in love with each other...
Rinko
Falling in love only adds to your troubles, right？
What's this all of a sudden？
Like I said, isn't it troublesome？
But there are also a lot of good things. Like, being together makes you happy, right？
Yeah. But you also become selfish, insecure, and jealous. Doesn't that make falling in love a little depressing？
When you put it that way, I agree. But...
Rinko doesn't like it.
But, if you're saying selfish things or getting jealous for Rinko...
That definitely makes Rinko happy, you know...
Rinko
Isn't it happening soon？
What is...？
What？ Did you forget？
Did I make a promise for something？
As expected. Oh yeah... As you get older, you become more forgetful.
Sorry...
What are you apologizing for？
No, I was just... So, what is happening again？
What was it？ Hmm. How's this for a hint？ Think about what I said earlier carefully.
That was a hint？ Hmm...？
Rinko
Hey, is there anything you want right now？
I think I want a bit of a raise in my allowance.
...If that's how it is, how about consulting your mother？
That's not it. Like a CD or a book or something... Something tangible.
I see... Ah！ I'm craving potato chips！
Then go buy them yourself！
This is tough... It's not specific and not obvious...
If you want me to say it... Then I want your kiss, ▲小早川＊▲.
What...？ Do you want to be kicked？
Rinko
Let's continue our previous discussion. Have you given a thought about what you want？
Ah！ I totally forgot...
This might not be worth it...
Are you planning to give me something？
N-No, that's not it.
My classmate wanted to give a present to a guy and she consulted me...
Well, it's because Rinko has a boyfriend.
Well... For a present, the feeling of the one who's giving it is more important than the item itself.
What's with that？ You sounded pretty smug. Well, if you're fine with that then so is Rinko...
Huh？
Rinko
Ah, I just remembered...
What？
Well, your birthday is coming up, right？
You're right. My birthday is coming up.
Yeah. Do you have any plans for it？
I don't know yet.
What do you mean？
Aren't you gonna be with me on my birthday, ▲小早川＊▲？
W-What do you mean...？
Hehe, just kidding. You can expect something nice, okay？
Rinko
Ah... It's almost August, huh...？
It's right in the middle of summer.
August, huh...？
Hahaha, I know！ It's coming soon.
...W-What are you talking about？
Of course, your birthday, ▲小早川＊▲！
Hmm...
Eh？ Don't tell me you forgot about it.
I don't really care. There's nothing special about my birthday.
But, are you planning something surprising for me？
That's still a secret.
Hmm？ Then should I be looking forward to it？
Rinko
Hey, do you remember any of your birthdays when you were a kid？
Why？
For Rinko... There are only bad memories.
Bad memories？
Even on my birthday, my dad still had to work and wouldn't come home...
I see... That's sad.
When it's my birthday, I usually become overly sentimental.
I understand.
That's why I just want it to pass as soon as it is possible, so I don't have any more bad memories about it...
...We can create some good memories about it from now on, okay？
Don't try to show off！
It's coming soon.
Rinko
Rinko's birthday？
Yeah.
Eh？ So you remembered.
We've been talking about this. How could I forget！？
I'm too afraid to expect anything...
It'll be okay！
Then I'll wait and see.
Just leave it to me.
So this is what you call playing it safe, huh？
(I don't think so...)
Rinko
I'm looking forward to it~
A present？
I mean my birthday. But I'm thinking about the present too...
Present, huh...？
What is it？
It's...
Ah. No, no. I want to keep looking forward to it until the time arrives.
Well, okay.
Actually, what matters to me isn't the present, but the person I'll spend my birthday with.
I wish my birthday would come sooner.
Rinko
It's almost the day. You know which, right？
What was it？
You said that you wouldn't forget it.
Well... It's that day, right？
What day is it？
It just slipped my mind...
Rinko is always being forgotten about！
You don't have to be this mad...
Hah... I can't believe I've been with this guy for a year...
Ah... It's the day when you and I started dating, ▲小早川＊▲...
You're too slow！
(It's already been a year, huh...？)
Rinko
Somehow, we've been dating for almost a year, huh？
Yeah... Even now, we're still so lovey-dovey.
Lovey-dovey... Don't you feel embarrassed saying that？
I've been with my cute girlfriend for a year now. I'm getting used to things like that.
I'm not used to it... Is it weird that my heart still beats fast when I'm with you？
I don't think it's weird. My heart beats fast, too.
Eh？ Like when？
I don't know when you're gonna get mad at me, so my heart is always beating quickly...
What！？ Now, I'm so mad at you！
Just kidding. My heart is always beating fast when I'm with you. During our dates or when we just walk together, ▲小早川＊▲.
Don't pretend to say something nice！
Rinko
We've been together for almost a year.
Yeah...
Do you love Rinko？
...I want to ask you the same thing, too, ▲小早川＊▲.
But Rinko asked you first！
Well, okay. Then we are going to answer this simultaneously, okay？
Okay. One, two...
I love you！
I really really love you！
Yay！ Rinko won！
That's not fair！
Rinko
We've been together for almost a year now.
When we look back, a year passed by so fast...
"I've been with this girl for a whole year." Do you feel like that？
What？ It's just one year. Good things will start from now, right？
Really...？ Well, I guess so.
Then how about？ What do you think, ▲小早川＊▲？
I've been enduring it.
That's cruel...
If I didn't, I would've moved in with you already. Would that be okay？
That might be nice in the future...
(Someday, okay？ ...)
Rinko
Hey, you know？
Yeah？
I've been thinking about this now and then...
...Is Rinko good enough for you？
Don't ask such a weird question...
But Rinko is always selfish and is always causing you trouble...
If you aren't like that, then you aren't my ▲小早川＊▲.
Really...？
Yeah, really...
I see... Right.
Rinko
Hey, can I ask you again？
What？
Is it really okay for you to have Rinko as your girlfriend？
You don't really have to ask, you know...？
But, I feel very uneasy.
...If it's not you, it can't be anyone else, ▲小早川＊▲.
Really？
Yeah.
Really, really？
Really.
Do you... love Rinko？
Yes...
I'm so glad...
Rinko
Do you know why people fall in love？
I wonder... I've never thought about it.
People meet by chance and before they know it, they are in love...
Yeah...
It has something to do with astronomy, right？ That something like that would happen by chance...
Maybe.
I don't really believe in fate... But I'm really thankful to myself for falling in love with you.
Even with astronomical probabilities, you were the one that got chosen...
Rinko
It's stated in a book I read a long time ago...
Yeah？
That all human beings are already programmed to fall in love with someone.
Programmed？ Like in our genes？
Yeah. But you know, I don't think that's the only thing.
Then what else？
I don't know.
What...？
But, I think I might be able to know it soon...
I see...
If I'm with you, I'll know it someday...
Rinko
It's coming soon.
...What is？
Could it be that you actually forgot？
Did I really promise you something？
No, that's not the case.
Sorry...
You don't really have to apologize！
It's good for Rinko that you forgot, though.
Why？
Well, you'll know when the time comes. Just wait for it.
Rinko
Hey, is there anything that you want？
Why do you ask all of a sudden？
Umm... Right！ I'm thinking about giving my dad a present.
Your dad, huh...？ Well, to be safe, what about a necktie？
A necktie...？ Well, I'll remember that.
Well then, isn't there anything that you really want now？
Something that I want？
Yeah, anything. Just tell me.
I can't think of anything now... I'll think about it.
Okay. I'm counting on you.
Rinko
Ah, so about the present I was asking you before.
Sorry... I completely forgot...
Whaaat？ That's terrible...
But you know, there isn't anything I really want right now...
Really...？ There's really nothing that you want？
I'm totally satisfied that I can be with you now, ▲小早川＊▲！
Hmm... I'm happy, but it doesn't really help...
Hah...
Rinko
Speaking of which, your birthday is coming up, right？
You remembered...
Well, yeah... I'm your girlfriend, after all.
Oh, hey, have you ever celebrated your birthday with a girl before？
Yeah.
Eh...！？ Really...？ So you've already done something like that...
It was a class party back in grade school, though...
...What？
Are you angry？
Geez. But then, that means Rinko will be the first girl you'll spend your birthday with, right？
Well, I guess that's right.
Really？ Hehe. I'll be looking forward to it.
Rinko
Well, it's almost August, right？
It's getting hot.
August, you know...
Of course！ It's almost your birthday, right, ▲小早川＊▲'？
You remembered.
I was thinking that you might forget about it.
How could I？ It's my girlfriend's birthday.
Hehe. Thanks. Then I can start looking forward to something, right？
Of course.
Rinko
For some reason, I've been checking the calendar everyday.
It's almost your birthday, right？
Yeah. Ever since I was a little kid, I've always felt lonely on my birthday.
I have always dreamed to celebrate it with someone...
Is that so...？
No, I'm all right now. It's because I have my boyfriend with me.
Yeah, next year, and the years after, we'll always celebrate it together.
Hey, thanks. You made Rinko's dream come true...
Let's wait until it's your birthday, okay？
Okay...
Rinko
When it's your birthday, it means you're a step closer to becoming an adult, right？
That's right. You'll grow one year older.
Does Rinko still look like a kid？
You're not an adult yet, but... Sometimes you act like an adult...
But you still think that I'm more like a kid, right？
Well, you're younger than me...
Geez, age doesn't matter.
...But no matter how old you are, I think that you will always be cute ▲小早川＊▲.
Really？ ...Thanks.
Rinko
It's coming soon, huh？
I didn't forget. It's your birthday, right？
I didn't think you'd really forget but I just wanted to double-check.
I will absolutely never forget it.
That's right. Is there anything you wish for？
A present？
I wanted to keep it secret but it's probably better to give you something you really want.
To spend a birthday with the one she loves... would be the best present Rinko could ever ask for.
I know that.
So... you must stay by my side.
Rinko
Do you know what's coming soon？
There's something coming？
Do you mean... you forgot？
Sorry...
...Did you really forget？
Eh...？ It seems like I'm starting to remember something.
You lied！
Sorry, forgive me...
You've been dating Rinko for almost a year, soon...
Ah！ It's almost been a year！
I don't care！
(Time has gone by fast...)
Rinko
A year has gone by in a blink of an eye. What do you think about this past year？
It has been a good year.
Hehe... I think so, too.
You've always been by my side. It feels natural to have you around, ▲小早川＊▲.
Ah, I understand that feeling. So I'm like the air or water for you...
I think we both feel the same about each other's existence, right？
What if Rinko suddenly disappears one day？
I wouldn't be able to breathe. I'd be suffering...
If that time comes, Rinko will rescue you.
By doing mouth-to-mouth？
Geez, you idiot...！ You always make fun of me.
Hahaha...
Rinko
A year has gone by so fast.
Yeah, for this past year, you have changed, huh, ▲小早川＊▲？
Yeah, I've changed. Now I love you more and more.
That's... not what I meant. I meant you have become gentler.
You think so？ Hehe.
When we first met, you were quite rebellious and not cooperative at all.
Hey, we don't have to talk about that...
Sorry, sorry！
I think I'm much more honest about my feelings.
That's a good thing.
Though, I'm still a little bit rebellious. Just a little bit.
Rinko
You know, thank you for being with me throughout this past year...
Same here.
I think I've become a bit more mature by being with you...
Yeah, I think so, too.
I'm more open to accept anything that's different from what I thought.
And I think I've become more obedient...
It'll be nice if we can learn about these things together from now on.
Yeah. Rinko will become a wonderful lady one day. You have to be with her, okay？
This year, next year, and the years after, I will always want to be with you ▲小早川＊▲.
You will always be Rinko's wonderful boyfriend, right...？
Yeah. Let's be nice to each other from now on, too.
